No. 8 Elmwood provides flexible, high quality space to suit your business needs. The offices, which have recently undergone refurbishment, are located on Chineham Park, Basingstoke’s premier business park and a vibrant business community. The space is available to occupy straight away.

Located just minutes from Basingstoke town centre, Chineham Park is easily accessible for commuters with a range of public transport options close by.

Central 40 is a three storey flagship office building in the heart of Chineham Park, Basingstoke’s premier business location. The building has been designed to have excellent environmental credentials and is certified BREEAM ‘Very Good’. Located just minutes from Basingstoke town centre,
Chineham Park is easily accessible for commuters with a range of public transport options close by.

3 Elmwood currently under refurbishment which has been designed to be suitable for almost any business in need of an office, the flexible open floor plate will allow for a variety of fit out options and uses.

Located just minutes from Basingstoke town centre, Chineham Park is easily accessible for commuters with a range of public transport options close by.

8 Cedarwood is a ground floor office suite with suspended ceilings and carpeted throughout. It is available as a whole unit or split into two. The
suite includes a fitted meeting room and nine car parking spaces. Located just minutes from Basingstoke town centre, Chineham Park is easily accessible for commuters with a range of public transport options close by.

Chineham Park is situated in a strategic location immediately to the North of Basingstoke and the town's ring road and adjacent to the A33 (Reading). The Park is therefore well connected for access to both the M3 and M4 motorways at Junctions 6 and 11 respectively.

Elmwood 2 is a unique and inspiring open plan workspace, perfect for businesses with an edge. Located just minutes from Basingstoke town centre, Chineham Park is easily accessible for commuters with a range of public transport options close by.

3 Cedarwood provides flexible, open plan office accommodation.


The offices are located on Chineham Park, Basingstoke’s premier business park and a vibrant business community.

Chineham Park is one of the region’s most desirable business addresses. A delightful 90 acre parkland setting that’s a breath of fresh air for the people who work there. Equally accessible by car or bike, with superb public transport links too, including an exclusive free bus service connecting people directly to the nearby Basingstoke train station.
No. 4 Elmwood provides flexible, high quality space to suit your business needs. The offices are located on Chineham Park, Basingstoke’s premier business park and a vibrant business community.

5 Lindenwood is a two storey office building with excellent parking. It has been refurbished to provide an open plan space, along with 2 offices and fitted kitchenette to the first floor. Located just minutes from Basingstoke town centre, Chineham Park is easily accessible for commuters with a range of public transport options close by.

4 Lindenwood is a two storey office building with a ready to go first floor suite with generous car parking available. Located just minutes from Basingstoke town centre, Chineham Park is easily accessible for commuters with a range of public transport options close by.

3 Hazelwood provides a self-contained statement office building and high quality space to suit your needs. Chineham Park offers a vibrant business community in a welcoming setting. 3 Hazelwood is currently being refurbished to provide modern, high quality office space.

6 Lindenwood is a two storey office building with excellent parking. It has been refurbished to provide open plan, air conditioned accommodation to the ground floor, and a partially fitted space to the first floor. Located just minutes from Basingstoke town centre, Chineham Park is easily accessible for commuters with a range of public transport options close by.
